Text: interviewsVince Thanks for taking the time off to meet with me last week I did enjoy meeting you and your coworkers in the Research Group I do realize my background may not be the best fit for the type of work done in your division Ill be job hunting over the next several weeks and would really appreciate it if you could let let me know if something opens up at Enron Thanks again and best regards Ruwan Ruwan Jayasuriya Economics Department Rice University ruwan Houston TX
